data.description: Welcome to 129 Ocean Cove Drive, a charming coastal retreat nestled in the prestigious community of Jupiter, Florida. Located just moments away from pristine beaches, championship golf courses, pickleball, upscale shopping, and fine dining, this rarely available location offers convenience and luxury. Ocean Cove residents enjoy a private drive, community pool, private sidewalks and beautiful landscaping throughout the neighborhood. Don't miss your opportunity to call this Jupiter treasure home.
